{"tid":380813,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找揸Corolla121嘅巴絲，有關音響","createTime":"2017-08-30T11:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T13:11:41.000Z","uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3254781384d80e95bef9d26dfbfbd18470be74","tid":380813,"uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟最近買左架全原裝2003 121黎代步<br />\n我諗車機都係原裝（有cd md個部）<br />\n無usb無藍芽咁唯有用aux 3.5線聽歌<br />\n但佢出黎嘅聲會好拆，尤其係低音，例如係鼓聲<br />\n究竟係咪車機問題？定係喇叭問題？<br />\n換車機有無幫助？"},{"pid":"44ea96c21eb2e23fe25199c5b474ad135b8680a0","tid":380813,"uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"換喇叭比較有用 原裝corolla嗰套真係比你聽收音機 換完一定好大分別 當然換得就一定要換埋車機啦"},{"pid":"9bf85dff937461056bf56c76e3d525cd533af015","tid":380813,"uid":23891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:17:51.000Z","msg":"咁搞一搞大約要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6a32a3937063f21e161cbb2f6feff78ef960fc","tid":380813,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:36:21.000Z","msg":"speaker同機頭都要换。<br />\n<br />\n機頭想平就上淘寶揾 花冠 一體機，8舊至1200左右已經ok乜柒gps, dvd,後cam 都有哂，當然貴些少行android個堆會更好一些。<br />\nspeaker去ssp鴨記 揾個間賣spider音響的，又係3至5百， 平得黎叫用得下咁。<br />\n<br />\n前5吋  後6x9 ."},{"pid":"d4b1a21699fc80ea17f16434076ff0c51ada5f08","tid":380813,"uid":23891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"搭單問下我架錢七ae100有冇得搞<br />\n想手機播出黎聽下歌咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f426c89f8832c7161c80b77ff0879439f8e41e59","tid":380813,"uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"其實唔用大面板都無所謂<br />\n剩係想正常聽歌<br />\n如果比車房整，大約約錢？<br />\n有無相熟車房？"},{"pid":"ce0933fa2fc392d6ceb67dfbb99414b25b087c57","tid":380813,"uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19fc58